transaction

Class Transaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • transaction.Transaction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Periodable, java.lang.Comparable<Transaction>

    public class Transaction
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Transaction>, Periodable
    This class represents a Transaction of Stocks.

    A Transaction occurs when two Order(s) happen to match successfully:

    A 'Buy' Order and a 'Sell' Order.

    annotated with JAXB, to marshal / unmarshal a .xml file.

    Version:
    1.0
